{"id":3469,"date":"2024-05-09T22:29:40","date_gmt":"2024-05-09T15:29:40","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/?p=3469"},"modified":"2024-05-09T22:30:26","modified_gmt":"2024-05-09T15:30:26","slug":"chuyen-ve-chiec-ao-nhung-cua-ba-chua-xu-nui-sam","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/chuyen-ve-chiec-ao-nhung-cua-ba-chua-xu-nui-sam\/","title":{"rendered":"Chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o nhung c\u1ee7a B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Sau v\u1ebb r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o, l\u00e0 t\u1ea5m l\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh k\u00ednh c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n g\u1eedi g\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam (TP. Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c, t\u1ec9nh An Giang). Chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ec7t n\u00ean, d\u00e2ng l\u00ean b\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t t\u00edn ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng d\u00e2n gian v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng m\u00e3nh li\u1ec7t&#8230;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"648\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-12.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3483\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o nhung c\u1ee7a B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-12.jpeg 1000w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-12-280x180.jpeg 280w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-12-600x389.jpeg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>H\u1ec5 th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u00e1n \u00e1o cho\u00e0ng, m\u00e3o B\u00e0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y, t\u1ee9c l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch Mi\u1ebfu B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n. Nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc: Ngang 1,8m, d\u00e0i 2m, ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u nhung \u0111\u1ee7 m\u00e0u (nh\u01b0ng h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng ai d\u00e2ng \u00e1o m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng cho B\u00e0, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"672\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-20.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3491\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o nhung c\u1ee7a B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-20.jpeg 1000w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-20-600x403.jpeg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Theo truy\u1ec1n thuy\u1ebft, khi v\u00f9ng n\u00fai Sam c\u00f2n hoang vu, d\u00e2n l\u00e0ng l\u00ean n\u00fai ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n pho t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ed5 ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean b\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e1 sa th\u1ea1ch. Ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd 9 c\u00f4 g\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed3ng trinh m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0a B\u00e0 xu\u1ed1ng n\u00fai \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh l\u1eadp mi\u1ebfu th\u1edd, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 may \u00e1o cho B\u00e0. D\u1ea7n d\u1ea7n, phong t\u1ee5c d\u00e2ng \u00e1o c\u00fang B\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u01b0u truy\u1ec1n r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"654\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-3.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3474\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o nhung c\u1ee7a B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-3.jpeg 1000w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-3-870x570.jpeg 870w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-3-600x392.jpeg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1143\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-15.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3486\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o nhung c\u1ee7a B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-15.jpeg 1000w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-15-600x686.jpeg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Theo th\u1eddi gian, c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o c\u0169ng d\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c may v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, \u0111\u00ednh h\u1ed9t \u0111\u00e1, c\u01b0\u1eddm l\u1ea5p l\u00e1nh, k\u1ef3 c\u00f4ng h\u01a1n; t\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh r\u1ed3ng, ph\u1ee5ng, h\u1ea1c\u2026, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn tr\u00ean n\u1ec1n v\u1ea3i nhung. M\u1ed7i chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o lo\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ebf n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 kho\u1ea3ng 1,8 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng. \u00c1o c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u nhung tuy\u1ebft ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u00ednh \u0111\u00e1 m\u1eafc ti\u1ec1n, c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 t\u1eeb 6 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ebfn 30 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng\/b\u1ed9 (bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 m\u00e3o, h\u00e0i).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"680\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-19.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3490\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o nhung c\u1ee7a B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-19.jpeg 1000w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-19-600x408.jpeg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"688\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-17.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3488\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o nhung c\u1ee7a B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-17.jpeg 1000w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-17-600x413.jpeg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1227\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-21.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3492\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o nhung c\u1ee7a B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-21.jpeg 1000w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-21-600x736.jpeg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1260\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-10.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3481\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o nhung c\u1ee7a B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-10.jpeg 1000w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-10-600x756.jpeg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc m\u00e3o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00f4ng phu, \u0111\u1ee7 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc, ki\u1ec3u d\u00e1ng, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1eb7ng t\u1eeb 2-3kg \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0i ch\u1ee5c kg. M\u00e3o th\u01b0\u1eddng gi\u00e1 1,8 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng; lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1eaft ti\u1ec1n h\u01a1n c\u00f3 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 6 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng ch\u1ee5c tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p \u00e1o, m\u00e3o, h\u00e0i c\u00f9ng m\u00e0u, ho\u1eb7c kh\u00e1c m\u00e0u, t\u00f9y theo nhu c\u1ea7u.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"689\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-4.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3475\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o nhung c\u1ee7a B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-4.jpeg 1000w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-4-600x413.jpeg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Hi\u1ec7n nay, to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 nhung y c\u00fang b\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gia c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb TP. H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh, ch\u1ee9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Theo ch\u1ecb Nh\u01b0 (c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng An B\u00ecnh, \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Ho\u00e0ng Di\u1ec7u), nh\u1eefng v\u1eadt ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1n \u0111\u1eaft nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0o d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m, khi nhu c\u1ea7u c\u00fang l\u1ec5, tr\u1ea3 l\u1ec5 &nbsp;B\u00e0 t\u0103ng cao.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"758\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-2.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3473\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o nhung c\u1ee7a B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-2.jpeg 1000w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-2-600x455.jpeg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Anh Tr\u1ea7n Minh \u0110\u0103ng (ng\u1ee5 ph\u01b0\u1eddng V\u0129nh Ngu\u01a1n,\u00a0TP. Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c) th\u01b0\u1eddng t\u00ecm mua c\u00e1c v\u1eadt ph\u1ea9m c\u00fang B\u00e0 theo th\u00f4ng l\u1ec7 h\u00e0ng n\u0103m c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh. \u201cM\u1eabu m\u00e3 r\u1ea5t phong ph\u00fa, gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 c\u0169ng t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u, n\u01a1i b\u00e1n, n\u00ean t\u00f4i th\u01b0\u1eddng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u nhi\u1ec1u c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1eb7t mua\u201d \u2013 anh \u0110\u0103ng chia s\u1ebb.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"663\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-11.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3482\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o nhung c\u1ee7a B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-11.jpeg 1000w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-11-600x398.jpeg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Ngay gi\u1eefa ch\u00e1nh \u0111i\u1ec7n, B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam \u0111\u1ed9i m\u00e3o, m\u1eb7c \u00e1o cho\u00e0ng th\u00eau long ph\u1ee5ng, ng\u1ed3i uy nghi v\u1edbi n\u00e9t m\u1eb7t hi\u1ec1n h\u00f2a, ph\u00fac h\u1eadu. Theo Ban Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb L\u0103ng mi\u1ebfu n\u00fai Sam, theo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7, s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nhung y d\u00e2ng B\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u00fac l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 7.000 \u2013 8.000 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"722\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-13.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3484\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o nhung c\u1ee7a B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-13.jpeg 1000w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-13-600x433.jpeg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 ghi nh\u1eadn t\u1ea5m l\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch th\u1eadp ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, Ban Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n cho\u00e0ng c\u00f9ng l\u00fac nhi\u1ec1u chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o cho B\u00e0. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi \u00e1o th\u00eau t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i c\u1ea7u k\u1ef3, chi\u1ebfm di\u1ec7n t\u00edch, ch\u1ec9 m\u1eb7c t\u1ed1i \u0111a 3 chi\u1ebfc\/l\u1ea7n. C\u00f2n \u00e1o th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1eb7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 7-8 chi\u1ebfc\/l\u1ea7n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"694\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-7.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3478\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o nhung c\u1ee7a B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-7.jpeg 1000w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-7-600x416.jpeg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>H\u00e0ng th\u00e1ng, Ban Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c thay \u00e1o, m\u00e3o cho B\u00e0 2 l\u1ea7n: V\u00e0o t\u1ed1i 13, s\u00e1ng 14 \u00e2m l\u1ecbch; t\u1ed1i 28, s\u00e1ng 29 \u00e2m l\u1ecbch (th\u00e1ng thi\u1ebfu) ho\u1eb7c t\u1ed1i 29 s\u00e1ng 30 \u00e2m l\u1ecbch (th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ee7). \u00c1o, m\u00e3o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn theo h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c b\u1ed1c th\u0103m.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi may m\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho hay tr\u01b0\u1edbc, s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp l\u00e0m l\u1ec5 c\u00fang \u00e1o, m\u00e3o d\u00e2ng cho B\u00e0. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, 5 ng\u00e0y l\u1ec5 ch\u00ednh m\u00f9a V\u00eda B\u00e0 (t\u1eeb l\u1ec5 t\u1eafm b\u00e0 23\/4 \u00e2m l\u1ecbch \u0111\u1ebfn 27\/4 \u00e2m l\u1ecbch), ch\u1ec9 m\u1eb7c duy nh\u1ea5t 1 \u00e1o cho b\u00e0, v\u1eadt ph\u1ea9m c\u0169ng t\u1eeb qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh b\u1ed1c th\u0103m ch\u1ecdn l\u1ec5 v\u1eadt c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"661\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-9.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3480\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o nhung c\u1ee7a B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-9.jpeg 1000w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-9-600x397.jpeg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c B\u00e0 kho\u00e1c, sau khi \u201cxu\u1ed1ng \u00e1o\u201d s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadp h\u1ee3p l\u1ea1i, chuy\u1ec3n sang c\u00f4ng \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u1eaft ra l\u00e0m l\u1ed9c g\u1eedi t\u1eb7ng kh\u00e1ch vi\u1ebfng B\u00e0. Theo t\u00e2m linh, chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c B\u00e0 kho\u00e1c s\u1ebd mang \u0111\u1ebfn may m\u1eafn, t\u00e0i l\u1ed9c cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1eadn.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"659\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-6.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3477\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o nhung c\u1ee7a B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-6.jpeg 1000w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-6-600x395.jpeg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o \u0111\u1eb9p, c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb cao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u01b0u gi\u1eef t\u1ea1i ph\u00f2ng tr\u01b0ng b\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Mi\u1ebfu B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam. Nhi\u1ec1u chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 200 \u2013 300 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng, theo l\u1eddi ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2ng c\u00fang. C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m tr\u00fang, ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c cho B\u00e0, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o khu tr\u01b0ng b\u00e0y v\u00ec r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb9p.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"669\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3472\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o nhung c\u1ee7a B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-1.jpeg 1000w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-1-600x401.jpeg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Theo \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Phong, Ph\u00f3 Tr\u01b0\u1edfng ban Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb L\u0103ng mi\u1ebfu n\u00fai Sam, s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eadt ph\u1ea9m c\u00fang B\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, khu tr\u01b0ng b\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kham xu\u1ec3, \u0111ang \u0111\u1ecbnh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng, m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng th\u00eam. Nhi\u1ec1u chi\u1ebfc m\u00e3o k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1edbn h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u01b0u gi\u1eef ri\u00eang.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"652\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3471\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o nhung c\u1ee7a B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image.jpeg 1000w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-600x391.jpeg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"681\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-8.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3479\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o nhung c\u1ee7a B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-8.jpeg 1000w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-8-600x409.jpeg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Hi\u1ec7n, \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb m\u1edf c\u1eeda ph\u00f2ng tr\u01b0ng b\u00e0y t\u1eeb 7 gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn 17 gi\u1edd h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y, gi\u00fap du kh\u00e1ch thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n tham quan. \u0110a s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u1ea7m tr\u1ed3, th\u00edch th\u00fa tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o \u0111\u1ee7 m\u00e0u, k\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1 uy nghi, n\u1eb7ng tr\u0129u.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"667\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-16.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3487\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o nhung c\u1ee7a B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-16.jpeg 1000w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-16-600x400.jpeg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"668\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-18.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3489\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o nhung c\u1ee7a B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-18.jpeg 1000w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-18-600x401.jpeg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"685\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-14.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3485\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o nhung c\u1ee7a B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-14.jpeg 1000w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-14-600x411.jpeg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"654\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-5.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3476\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o nhung c\u1ee7a B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-5.jpeg 1000w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-5-870x570.jpeg 870w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-5-600x392.jpeg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Sau khi tham quan, c\u00fang vi\u1ebfng Mi\u1ebfu B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn l\u1ed9c mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u1ea3nh v\u1ea3i nhung tr\u01a1n ho\u1eb7c v\u1ea3i c\u00f2n k\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1, c\u01b0\u1eddm, c\u1eaft ra t\u1eeb \u00e1o B\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 kho\u00e1c. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u00f3n qu\u00e0 \u00fd ngh\u0129a d\u00e0nh t\u1eb7ng cho kh\u00e1ch du l\u1ecbch, gi\u00fap h\u1ecd th\u00eam ni\u1ec1m tin t\u00e2m linh, mong mu\u1ed1n quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i khu du l\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\">\n<p>Ngu\u1ed3n tham kh\u1ea3o<\/p>\n<cite>An Giang Online | <a href=\"https:\/\/baoangiang.com.vn\/chuyen-ve-chiec-ao-nhung-cua-ba-chua-xu-nui-sam-a365350.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https:\/\/baoangiang.com.vn\/chuyen-ve-chiec-ao-nhung-cua-ba-chua-xu-nui-sam-a365350.html<\/a><\/cite><\/blockquote>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Sau v\u1ebb r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o, l\u00e0 t\u1ea5m l\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh k\u00ednh c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n g\u1eedi g\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam (TP. Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c, t\u1ec9nh An Giang). Chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ec7t n\u00ean, d\u00e2ng l\u00ean b\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t t\u00edn ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng d\u00e2n gian v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng m\u00e3nh li\u1ec7t&#8230; H\u1ec5 th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u00e1n \u00e1o cho\u00e0ng, m\u00e3o [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":3470,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[131],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3469"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3469"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3469\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3494,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3469\/revisions\/3494"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3470"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3469"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=3469"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=3469"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}